<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6571517>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Quararibea alversonii. a. floriferous branch; b. leaf (abaxial surface); c. detail of pocket-like domatia; d. polar view of the bud, evidencing the costate calyx; e. flower; f. pedicel and calyx; g. staminal column; h. detail of the staminal column apex and anthers; i. immature fruit.Photos: C.D.M. Ferreira, based on A.M.Amorim 5696 (a, d), A.M. Amorim 5745 (b, c), R.P. Belém 1312 (e–h), and M.M.M. Lopes et al. 990 (i)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6571517/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6571519>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Detail of the floriferous branch of Quararibea alversonii. Photo: A.M. Amorim." ;
